1. **Single-pass verification**: The paper claims single-pass over video but Figure 3 and text suggest clips are processed sequentially. Clarify whether clips can truly be processed in parallel or if order matters, and whether frames are re-loaded multiple times.

2. **Training efficiency analysis**: The batch constraint (one video per batch to avoid race conditions) likely dramatically increases training time. Report total training time or steps needed to reach reported performance.

