## How to Improve This Paper

### Missing Experiments (top 3-5 only)
1. **No comparison to any existing OFA/NAS baselines applied to LLMs.** The paper claims to be the "first once-for-all" for LLMs but only compares to single-configuration methods (QA-LoRA, GPTQ). Compare against weight-sharing OFA with QAT to validate the claimed advantage of decoupling—without this, the core contribution is unvalidated.

